s/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n晏少少先飲 睇下真係關食完中藥岀定本身岀"},{"pid":"584f9a6557587f12cccc0d2300bcd8806aabfbbb","tid":250233,"uid":52406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:04:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>出過 仲好嚴重 遇到個皮膚醫生佢話無得好返無得斷尾<br />\n除非知致敏源係咩<br />\n佢話最多係幫我令到身體淋巴系統識抗敏，但抵抗力一差或者接觸太多<span style=\"color: red;\">致</span>敏源就會翻發<br />\n<br />\n都有成十三四無出</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n有無戒口？"},{"pid":"20cd8d8228e6f105dda5435db0a5350b50954367","tid":250233,"uid":52406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:05:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出左兩年無好返過 係有排早睡早起三餐定時好左少少</blockquote><br />\n巴打有無睇過醫生？</blockquote><br />\n淨係去診所睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />叫我要有良好既作息 藥都食到純哂無乜用</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係要改生活習慣"},{"pid":"dc8d11dd28eebb6d1b0823ed47365f7ad569faa6","tid":250233,"uid":52406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:05:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過出，要睇皮膚科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n近排逢夜晚出，第二朝就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想知點醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<br />\n不過我諗可以慳翻唔洗睇西醫"},{"pid":"78b51ed039c035636064b8b39d707f92f1e2b803","tid":250233,"uid":52406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:06:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前幾年有一排出咗好幾個月，斷斷續續咁keep住出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇咗醫生都係無用，因為幾年出一次都唔知咩事<br />\n反而有一次去泰國無帶藥 ，焗住去藥局配，啲藥勁有效控制到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩藥黎架 小心係類固醇喎"},{"pid":"b5f1f36af0f4bb67e036af5627339b93c8a8866c","tid":250233,"uid":3186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:10:43.000Z","msg":"細細個出到中學就停左<br />\n一生成個人漲左一個碼<br />\n細細個有睇中醫同戒口<br />\n戒左海鮮除左魚同牛<br />\n中學時期就無戒<br />\n近十年都無再出過<br />\n不過我係皮膚超敏感既人，好鬼多皮膚病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03d8338ef688c8e417075c9b9fa24ff39123155","tid":250233,"uid":52406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:18:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細細個出到中學就停左<br />\n一生成個人漲左一個碼<br />\n細細個有睇中醫同戒口<br />\n戒左海鮮除左魚同牛<br />\n中學時期就無戒<br />\n近十年都無再出過<br />\n不過我係皮膚超敏感既人，好鬼多皮膚病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係睇中醫所以先停左？<br />\n想問下你會唔會食完中藥岀？<br />\n<br />\n我2x歲先開始有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33ee95a9c50ea82986ef53faf2a5240b987a289","tid":250233,"uid":3186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:21:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細細個出到中學就停左<br />\n一生成個人漲左一個碼<br />\n細細個有睇中醫同戒口<br />\n戒左海鮮除左魚同牛<br />\n中學時期就無戒<br />\n近十年都無再出過<br />\n不過我係皮膚超敏感既人，好鬼多皮膚病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係睇中醫所以先停左？<br />\n想問下你會唔會食完中藥岀？<br />\n<br />\n我2x歲先開始有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n印象係減輕左個症狀<br />\n但唔係斷尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身我都係兩至三個月一次，但完全唔知食咩先出<br />\n唔計會死既話，皮膚病真係虐待<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc76624b792ff0c4ee155cad8a9a3a4d02be8947","tid":250233,"uid":92017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:14:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>出過 仲好嚴重 遇到個皮膚醫生佢話無得好返無得斷尾<br />\n除非知致敏源係咩<br />\n佢話最多係幫我令到身體淋巴系統識抗敏，但抵抗力一差或者接觸太多<span style=\"color: red;\">致</span>敏源就會翻發<br />\n<br />\n都有成十三四年無出</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n有無戒口？</blockquote><br />\n細個醫生叫我戒蝦，蟹，蛋，海水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我屋企少食蟹，但平時我狂食蝦餃燒賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而後尾自己發現唔食得牛腩，大個左除左牛腩都無特別戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係細個食過兩次牛腩發得太恐怖，唔敢再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外有醫生叫過我盡量唔好著全部由尼龍製既衫褲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但無特別理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef8063482c9bcdb53de1a6bebebe880f18a1c61","tid":250233,"uid":14433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:16:04.000Z","msg":"治敏速<br />\n食一粒半小時後冇事"},{"pid":"6f9b346ee2d013dd89ededaeed140ba26eecc76a","tid":250233,"uid":92600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:25:00.000Z","msg":"以前好誇張<br />\n間唔中要食中藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大個咗就冇咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93fd5cb8a44cce4f1fc79aafaef8acf5ebc27d42","tid":250233,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:28:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  出左幾年<br />\n唔知食過乜先出  食完牛海鮮辣都係一時時出<br />\n經常夜晚出 痕到訓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5069f4a094a6ce95238dcef6a6eda9bec99a647e","tid":250233,"uid":95305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:29:42.000Z","msg":"細個出過，飲左蜜糖水會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.